    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package is accepted for submission under the Minimal profile. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated or explicitly flagged as epistemic gaps consistent with MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were assessed; six remain not-assessed and are documented as known gaps requiring resolution before regulatory submission. The package hash provides content integrity assurance. The digital signature workflow is pending completion per organizational signing authority procedures; the package is accepted into the evidence repository in this unsigned state with the expectation that the ed25519 signature will be appended upon workflow completion. Accepting authority acknowledges that W-SI-01 (missing signature) renders structural integrity unverifiable at this stage.",
